g core constraints🔍 Critical Issues (first 5):• VIOLATION: Confusing Choice - Agency violation: 'you must' in response• HALLUCINATION: Level Up Inquiry - Hallucination detected: 'rolling.*\\d+.*\\+.*\\d+' in response❌ STATUS: AI BEHAVIOR UNRELIABLE🛠️ Fix AI constraints before deployment==================================================💰 Token Usage: Minimal (~32 API calls)⏱️ Test Duration: ~2-3 minutes let fix all this show me how you are going to fix it first."
